  .primary-container-hero
    .hero-card
      .hero-text
        h1.hero.white Ditch the <span class='strike'>survey.</span> Measure engagement instantly.
        h4.hero.white Skipper shows HR teams how they can measure and maximize engagement and productivity for their company... <i>without sending a single survey.</i>
        form#demoHeroForm(action="/request-demo2.html" method="GET")
          input.input-box.input-nav(type="email" placeholder="Enter email" name="email")
          input#email_submit.button.button-nav(type="submit" value="Request Demo")
      .hero-image
        img.hero-img(src=imgpath + 'index2-hero.png')
        
    .primary-container.centered
      h1.hero Powered by AI, designed for HR.
      h4 Through powerful artificial intelligence methods like <a target="_blank" href="https://nlp.stanford.edu/sentiment/"><span class="code">Sentiment Analysis</span></a> and <a target="_blank" href="https://dspace.mit.edu/handle/1721.1/7290"><span class="code">Support Vector Machines</span></a>, Skipper quickly analyzes employee engagement and productivity. 

      br
      br
      br
      br
      
      .container.moat
        .row.show
          .col-md-9
            img.large.shadow#prim(src=imgpath + "home-demo.png")
          .col-md-3
            .card.child.shadow#one
              h1 Customized goals
              h4 Set goals for new HR and people operations initiatives so you can measure how effective they are in your own terms.

            .card.child.shadow#two
              h1 Measure Success
              h4 See how management decisions, policy changes, and benefits affect employee engagement.

            .card.child.shadow#three
              h1 Actionable Advice
              h4 Learn which groups within your company are disengaging, and see advice on how to re-engage them.

